{"tid":539224,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"「少圖」Sydney 幾日鳩行鳩影","createTime":"2018-01-24T11:11:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-24T15:48:40.000Z","uid":76020,"like":6,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"41b6088a86c0d8c982359a5c629252667255fcc3","tid":539224,"uid":76020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T11:11:50.000Z","msg":"HDD 冇撚晒位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 要黎緊幾日清左或者買左外置先可以再po，純粹分享下。有咩意見隨便講，不喜勿屌太勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n悉尼Central 車站隨影，機場出黎轉車好似必經。但係落左車先發現原來唔駛落可以直到目的地，只係路線名會改<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 白白走左班車<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/24/190313_d19387578371c2826e54ccf3d4713e1a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F24%2F190313_d19387578371c2826e54ccf3d4713e1a.png&h=04ca302e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n到左酒店擺低野已經黃昏，不過依到日落好慢，照出去行下。悉尼都有個Hyde Park，好多細路玩波<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/24/190643_83ae4194c23390651fedfea28e5c27ad.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F24%2F190643_83ae4194c23390651fedfea28e5c27ad.png&h=6933e339&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n直接向海港果邊行，經過另一個公園，日落光係CBD 高樓大廈入面射出黎咁<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/24/190819_413d28fd6bfb701c52863c801f41675a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F24%2F190819_413d28fd6bfb701c52863c801f41675a.png&h=b5e0e480&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n旅客相唔po啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  原來澳洲都有地方可以咁迫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/24/190959_c19d946c4ae65c31c1936428ae5dd5e5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F24%2F190959_c19d946c4ae65c31c1936428ae5dd5e5.png&h=f1835e55&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n到果日係星期六，鬼佬weekend 一定要去酒吧的，Opera House 出面的bar 人山人海<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/24/191129_48c7d630a9b20a54e40ac7d91b3a7c98.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F24%2F191129_48c7d630a9b20a54e40ac7d91b3a7c98.png&h=a2691a61&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e7778221ad16f7d174b460fb52628aa6add4921c","tid":539224,"uid":121374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T15:48:40.000Z","msg":"留個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好想去多次悉尼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}